sentences: Martin Stephani (2 November 1915 – 9 June 1983) was a German conductor and professor.

After a position of music director of the city of Wuppertal, he was from 1957 to 1980 a professor of conducting at the Hochschule für Musik Detmold, serving as the institute's president from 1959 to 1982.
